&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;As we transition from a service-oriented model to a product-driven platform, we are expanding our hybrid Bengaluru based team. We are looking for a Lead Applied AI Engineer to help advance the next chapter of Konovo’s AI-native platform.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
